8  |  DISCOVERY QUESTIONS — Surface BASSnet weaknesses naturally

Ask without naming BASSnet. Expose gaps that favour AMOS™.

•	The vendor's new cloud platform launched recently — how long has it been in live production in environments with the same safety-critical complexity as yours?
•	Is the platform purpose-built for asset management and compliance, or is it a maritime ERP that includes those as modules?
•	Do maintenance, compliance, and governance data all live in one database — or does the intelligence layer require integration between the ERP and a BI tool?
•	When you need multi-entity governance reporting across regions at board level — have you seen that demonstrated at your fleet's scale?
•	What is your current three-way invoice match rate — and what does a failed match cost in investigation time per incident?
•	How much procurement spend variance do you carry per quarter — and can you see it in real time at the point of requisition approval?
•	What does your current class society approval picture look like — and does your system support vessels under multiple societies without gaps?
•	Can you speak to a reference customer in your sector who has been live on the current platform for 5+ years at your fleet's complexity level?
•	When the vendor describes their cybersecurity posture — what does that mean for your operational data sovereignty and where it is hosted?

